title: Monday 13-02-2012 Days of our Lives.avi
description:
Abby spots Carrie and Austin kissing, and runs off.



Mel bumps into Abby, who spills the beans. Melanie is shocked and comforts her friend.



Will tells Rafe that Sami's crazy, and not to worry about kissing Carrie because it wasn't a big deal.



Carrie isn't able to have sex with Austin.



Bo questions a perp, hoping to nab his boss, some big mobster named Maroni.



Roman learns Rafe kissed Carrie and has a fit.



Brady is astounded to learn that Ian's Madi's husband. He runs out on her.
